    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older vehicle in good overall condition. It shows some normal light wear for its age, but it presents nicely inside and out and feels like a solid, dependable car for someone who wants a clean, usable vehicle without paying premium money for a mint example. Buyers can expect a car that has been maintained reasonably well, with a tidy appearance, comfortable interior, and only the kind of minor cosmetic flaws you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle of this age.",
