      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with great value for the price. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it offers a practical option for buyers seeking a low-cost car they can drive, improve, or use as a dependable backup. An excellent opportunity to get into a vehicle without overspending.",
