    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s not winning any beauty contests, but it still has plenty to offer for someone who wants affordable wheels or a solid project. It starts, runs, and gives you a practical way to get around without spending a fortune. Great fit for a first-time buyer on a budget, a commuter, or anyone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of wear in exchange for real value. Priced to move and worth a look if you want simple, usable transportation.",
      "price": 5900.0,
