    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with strong value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. This car shows its age cosmetically and will need attention, but it still offers a sturdy platform with a responsive powertrain, predictable road manners, and plenty of life for a hands-on owner. Good candidate for a daily beater, weekend tinkering, or parts donor depending on your plans. If you want inexpensive entry into ownership with room to improve it your way, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
